data.description: Have you been looking for luxury on the northeast side of town? If so, this home is for you! This 3/2 has beautiful waterproof, vinyl flooring installed throughout the home. Both bathrooms are complete with a tiled walk-in shower and cobblestone bases. The master bath has a separate soaking tub and two large closets! The kitchen is a chef’s dream with plenty of space to prepare food on your elegant granite countertops. More cabinets and a butcher block counter have been installed in the adjoining room to allow for extra storage and buffet style entertaining. Now, let’s skip to the good part… there is a 2000 sqft oakwood pool room off the main living area boasting an in-ground pool, spa/hot tub, and dry bar! The many skylights and two sets of double doors opening to the patio give you that outdoor feel with plenty of sunlight. There is a large covered patio, shed, and grass area out back. You do not want to miss out on this stunning property! Call today to schedule your private showing.
